body:
Although not all clients will use the Normandy-provided implementations, would it be good to provide a URL to the API that provides the implementation here? Something like

``` yaml
recipes: [
    {
        name: "heartbeat.australis.1"
        actions: [
            name: "show_survey"
            impl_hash: "4011cf569f3639b9069fc2c50117d3f8597e83c61be2014081ad06ee0fe427c2"
            url: "https://shield.mozilla.org/api/v1/actions/show_survey/"
        ]
    }
]
```
